parameters.name: jobId
parameters.description: The ID of the batch prediction job.

parameters.name: inputPath
parameters.description: The Amazon S3 location of your training file.

parameters.name: outputPath
parameters.description: The Amazon S3 location of your output file.

parameters.name: eventTypeName
parameters.description: The name of the event type.

parameters.name: iamRoleArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the IAM role to use for this job request. The IAM Role must have read permissions to your input S3 bucket and write permissions to your output S3 bucket. For more information about bucket permissions, see User policy examples in the Amazon S3 User Guide.

parameters.name: tags
parameters.description: A collection of key and value pairs. (dict) --- A key and value pair. A tag key. A value assigned to a tag key.

nested_params.name: value
nested_params.description: A value assigned to a tag key.
